		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It turns off the screen half way through, uses Sprite DMA from ROM to clear the sprite table, then writes some new sprites using the PPU registers, and no DMA.
<br />
<br />The MMC1 version is more sane, it just changes the nametable and scrolls.  Nothing crazy.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


